---
export const prerender = true;

import LogoWithTextVertical from "../assets/logoWithTextVertical.svg";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import DashboardButton from "../components/DashboardButton.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Shell from "../layouts/Shell.astro";
---

<Shell>
	<Fragment slot="head">
		<title>
			craftlions | Modern Freelance IT Services, Technical Advisory & Product
			Development
		</title>
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="Craftlions delivers modern IT services, technical advisory, pair programming, workshops, and high-quality digital solutions for businesses that want reliable expertise without overpriced agencies or unreliable freelancers."
		>
		<meta
			name="keywords"
			content="IT services, technical advisory, freelance developer, software consultant, modern web development, pair programming, workshops, asynchronous collaboration, future-proof technology, external technical expertise, software architecture, digital product development"
		>
		<meta
			property="og:title"
			content="Craftlions | Modern IT Services & Technical Advisory"
		>
		<meta
			property="og:description"
			content="Reliable, high-quality IT services and technical expertise for businesses that want innovation, flexibility, and long-term success."
		>
		<meta property="og:type" content="website">
	</Fragment>
	<Fragment slot="body">
		<body
			class="min-h-dvh grid grid-rows-[auto_1fr_auto] bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-950 dark:text-neutral-50 text-neutral-950 antialiased gap-12 p-4 text-pretty"
		>
			<header class="grid gap-6 justify-items-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<nav class="py-6 grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr] w-full">
					<LogoWithTextVertical
						class="h-28 col-start-2"
						style="view-transition-name: nav-logo;"
					/>
					<section class="justify-self-end">
						<DashboardButton server:defer>
							<span class="px-6 py-3 font-bold" slot="fallback">
								Loading...
							</span></DashboardButton
						>
					</section>
				</nav>
				<section class="grid gap-4">
					<h1 class="font-black text-3xl border-l-2 pl-3 border-l-cyan-500">
						Modern IT services for ambitious companies
					</h1>
					<p class="pl-3">
						craftlions revolutionizes IT services with unmatched passion,
						dedication, and a pratical innovative mindset. We help businesses by
						delivering modern digital solutions, technical advisory, and
						future-proof decisions designed for real business outcomes.
					</p>
					<p class="pl-3">
						From product development and technical strategy to workshops, and
						hands-on delivery, Craftlions brings external expertise that
						integrates seamlessly into your existing processes. Our focus is
						simple:
						<strong>
							top-tier quality, customer satisfaction, and innovative ideas that
							help you stay ahead of the competition.
						</strong>
					</p>
				</section>
				<section>
					<a href="mailto:alexander@craftlions.com">
						<Button type="button"> Start your project with us </Button>
					</a>
				</section>
			</header>

			<main
				class="w-full grid content-start min-h-0 pl-3 max-w-3xl mx-auto gap-12"
			>
				<!-- <section class="text-center flex flex-col gap-2">
					<h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Trusted by:</h3>
					<ul class="grid grid-flow-col gap-6">
						<li>Cloudflare</li>
						<li>Astro</li>
						<li>AWS Amplify</li>
						<li>Google Cloud Platform</li>
					</ul>
				</section> -->
				<section class="grid gap-6">
					<h2 class="font-extrabold text-2xl">
						Services reimagined to exceed modern innovative expectations
					</h2>
					<article class="grid gap-3">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">
							State-of-the-art software development
						</h3>
						<p>
							craftlions specializes in innovative and modern technologies to
							ensure every project is future-proof, scalable and maintainable
							and built to industry standards. The result is software that
							performs exceptionally well today and remains valuable tomorrow.
						</p>
					</article>
					<article class="grid gap-3">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Flexible & Asynchronous</h3>
						<p>
							Prefer fewer unproductive meetings and more momentum? So do we.
							craftlions supports flexibility that matches your preferences,
							strcutrures and processes. We embrace an async-first approach, but
							are always available for real-time collaboration when needed. We
							adapt to your rhythm, not the other way around, to ensure smooth
							communication and efficient progress without unnecessary
							disruptions.
						</p>
					</article>
					<article class="grid gap-3">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">
							Technical Advisory & Strategic Guidance
						</h3>
						<p>
							Strong products require more than code. craftlions helps you make
							smarter technical decisions with confidence. We provide external
							expertise to evaluate ideas, define clear implementation paths,
							and ensure your technical direction supports your goals. We help
							you choose solutions that support growth, reduce future risk, and
							create solutions that are truly unique.
						</p>
					</article>
					<article class="grid gap-3">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Workshops & Continuous Learning</h3>
						<p>
							Great results come from strong teams and knowledge-sharing. We
							support continuous learning through workshops. craftlions offers
							teams the opportunity to learn from our expertise, stay up-to-date
							with the latest technologies, and develop skills that empower them
							to build better products and make informed technical decisions.
						</p>
					</article>
					<section>
						<a href="mailto:alexander@craftlions.com">
							<Button type="button"> Learn more about our services </Button>
						</a>
					</section>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-6">
					<h2 class="font-extrabold text-2xl">Why choose craftlions?</h2>
					<p>
						At craftlions, quality is not an afterthought. it is the foundation
						of everything we do. We beleive that balancing innovation,
						maintainability, performance and business value are key factors to
						success.
					</p>
					<ul>
						<li>
							* Years of experience with modern technology across multiple
							sectors
						</li>
						<li>
							* Professionals with a proven track record of reliable delivery
						</li>
						<li>
							* High innovative thinking with practicallity and technical depth
						</li>
						<li>
							* Individualized solutions tailored to your business goals and
							operational realities
						</li>
						<li>
							* A commitment to quality, customer satisfaction, and long-term
							success
						</li>
						<li>
							* Seamless integration with your processes, tools, and preferred
							ways of working
						</li>
						<li>* Commitment to top-tier quality in every engagement</li>
						<li>
							* A clear standard: we only undertake tasks we are confident we
							can deliver at exceptional quality
						</li>
					</ul>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-6">
					<h2 class="font-extrabold text-2xl">
						Let's build something better together
					</h2>
					<p>
						craftlions helps businesses build smarter with modern IT services,
						technical advisory, and hands-on product development support.
						Whether you need a reliable technology partner, software
						architecture expertise, or strategic technical guidance, we create
						practical, scalable solutions built for long-term success.
					</p>
					<p>
						We approach every project with curiosity, clarity, and full
						ownership. By challenging outdated thinking and introducing fresh,
						effective ideas, craftlions helps move your business forward with
						confidence. From technical strategy and system architecture to
						collaborative product development, our work is focused on delivering
						results that exceed expectations.
					</p>
					<p>
						Our mission goes beyond writing code. We help you strengthen your
						technical foundation, make better technology decisions, reduce
						unnecessary complexity, and build products and systems designed to
						last. That is what future-proof services should deliver:
						reliability, maintainability, and real business value.
					</p>
					<p>
						Every solution we create is shaped around quality, innovation, and
						customer satisfaction. We align technical decisions with your
						business goals, minimize risk, and prepare your company for
						sustainable growth. By combining modern technologies with proven
						engineering practices, craftlions helps you stay competitive without
						compromising stability or performance.
					</p>
					<p>
						If you are looking for a technical partner that brings external
						expertise, strategic clarity, creative problem-solving, and a
						commitment to high-quality delivery, craftlions is ready to help.
						Get in touch to discuss your project, challenge, or idea, and
						discover how we can help you move faster, build smarter, and achieve
						better technical outcomes.
					</p>
					<section>
						<a href="mailto:alexander@craftlions.com">
							<Button type="button"> Get in touch. </Button>
						</a>
					</section>
				</section>
			</main>
			<Footer />
		</body>
	</Fragment>
</Shell>
